originalText.text: We just bought our first condo in the city and was very fortunate to have used Catherine as our realtor.  Her thorough knowledge of the local housing market, incredible patience, expert guidance and straight forward advice made finding our new home a  stress-free, successful, fun process. She was always prompt in answering all our questions, looking out for our best interest which enabled us to build a trustworthy relationship.  We are grateful that Cathy guided us through this process and helped us secure our dream home.

originalText.text: I bought my first home just recently and Catherine was an excellent broker to work with. She was warm and gracious as well as straightforward and concise in advising me on how to navigate the home buying process. She was always quick to respond to my questions (of which there were many) and I always had the sense that she was giving me reasonable, objective guidance on certain very difficult challenges. Highly recommended and I'm very happy with my real estate purchase!

originalText.text: Catherine is a gem!!! She was so helpful with renting our apartment during COVID. It was a tough time and she was able to get us a renter so quickly, and was VERY hands on with the entire process to ensure it was seamless and turned around quickly.  I really appreciate how much she communicates so everyone is well informed.  We couldn’t recommend her more!!
